No. 10-10900. Juan Pantoja, Petitioner v. Florida. 565 U.S. 1009, 132 S. Ct. 496,

181 L. Ed. 2d 389,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7688. October 31, 2011.

Motion of Florida Association of Criminal Defense Lawyers for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Florida denied.

Same case below, 59 So. 3d 1092.
